title: XSitePro2 with ResourcePack
description:
XsitePro2 (v2.5.5) with ResourcePack

I made this installer to automate the installation and activation.

Inside the package are the official installers running in silent mode.

This package will no work on windows xp due to scripting errors, tested on windows 7 may work on windows 10.

This software is discontinued now, which is a shame.

package can also be run in silent mode with /qn switch.

Please leave comments.

No Virus no spyware adware etc
